oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Cycloaddition of substituted spiroepoxycyclohexa-2,4-dienones: synthesis and X-ray crystal structure of the adducts
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: SINGH, VISHWAKARMA
TOSH, DILIP K
KANE, VINAYAK V
ERNST, LUDGER
JONES, PETER G
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: cycloaddition
crystal structure
x-ray crystallography
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The syntheses of the tricyclic ketoepoxides 1 and 2 from the readily available aromatic precursors 5 and 6 via cycloaddition of the spiroepoxycyclohexa-2,4-dienones 3 and 4 are described. The crystal structures of 1 and 2 were determined.
